创建一个名称为“筛选条件”的选择屏幕
  选择屏幕字段有:工厂（T001W-WERKS):必输，默认值为E100
                 库存地点（T001L-LGORT):必输
                 过账日期(默认为系统当前日期）：必输，并使其不接受输入，但输入域可见
                 成本中心（CSKT-KOSTL)：
                 物料（MARA-MATNR)  MATNR1  TO   MATNR2
                 物料组（T023T-WGBEZ) WGBEZ1 TO  WGBEZ2
                 
                 
                 
                 
                  
 tables:mara,t023t.

selection-screen begin of block test with frame title text-001.

parameters p1 type t001w-werks obligatory default 'E100'.
parameters p2 type t001l-lgort obligatory.
parameters p3 type d obligatory default sy-datum modif id gg.
parameters p4 type cskt-kostl.

select-options sp1 for mara-matnr default '1010000001' to '1010000020'.
select-options sp2 for t023t-wgbez default '原材料' to '成品物料'.

selection-screen end of block test.

at selection-screen output.

  loop at screen.
    if screen-group1 = 'GG'.
      screen-input = '0'.
      screen-invisible = '0'.
    endif.
    modify screen.
  endloop.                